{"tid":25481,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人同我一樣成日比銀行打嚟叫你升級個戶口","createTime":"2016-12-06T06:52:14.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-29T13:34:00.000Z","uid":20419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a8fe22f6dd04b38260f8b0b56350cd1daf3f8764","tid":25481,"uid":20419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T06:52:14.000Z","msg":"銀行成日打嚟叫你升級個戶口又話唔收服務費唔收年費<br />\n其實會唔會有伏?<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打知道究竟點解係咁會有人打嚟叫你升？"},{"pid":"a76bc94b38f678952240fd9863cf8a5dbd133d8a","tid":25481,"uid":20419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T06:55:33.000Z","msg":"問佢有無存款限制 佢話有 但又話可以括免 <br />\n咁姐係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ae8293730fccb549c4fd1afcdcdceb518d2add6","tid":25481,"uid":2267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T07:07:20.000Z","msg":"姐係要你acc有指定最低款項（如最少有$5,000係戶口，每間銀行有唔同最低限額），亦都可以簡單啲嚟講：你已買咗佢acc。如果你係指定日期內無佢指定嘅錢係戶口，佢會以你戶口不足嘅限額嚟扣你錢。<br />\n扣幾多就以每間銀行收費；當然你申請咗會方便你戶口用途，如：網上登入戶口乜乜物物。<br />\n<br />\n利申：鳩up"},{"pid":"9b6a37979663e63b03efc0c4f3db95dff0cc97c8","tid":25481,"uid":20419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T00:42:55.000Z","msg":"姐係有伏？"},{"pid":"b0647a3038e0da5e1f28080171015405a90341bd","tid":25481,"uid":20419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T13:32:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d159b62703e1a1933760d939853345f6ac4e0d11","tid":25481,"uid":26354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-29T13:34:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n頭一年兩年咪免"}]}